{"about_the_game":"<strong>Groovy is a fast-paced precision platformer where you can manipulate the colors of the world. Avoid traps using speed boosts, jump boosts, and color powers alongside a robot surfer named Finn to defeat the Gloom.</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946460/extras/Groovy_ColorManipulating.png?t=1671818438\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946460/extras/ExtremeBoostArrowShowcase.gif?t=1671818438\" /><br>In Groovy you can manipulate the color of the world to alter the environment around you. This can be used to avoid traps, walk through walls and platforms, and more!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946460/extras/Groovy_TakeDownGloom.png?t=1671818438\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946460/extras/GloomLauncherShowcase.gif?t=1671818438\" /><br>The gloom has infested the world of Groovy! It is up to you and your robot companion, Finn, to take them down!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946460/extras/Groovy_ColorPalettes.png?t=1671818438\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946460/extras/ColorPaletteShowcase.gif?t=1671818438\" /><br>Everyone has their own preferences and, in a game about color, you should be able to choose the ones you look at. Choose from 15+ player colors and over 25 color palettes!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946460/extras/Groovy_Features.png?t=1671818438\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Single-player level campaign.<br></li><li> Color manipulating platforming. <br></li><li> Intense boss fights.<br></li><li> Collectable smileys within each level.<br></li><li> Reactive dialogue from Finn the robot.<br></li><li> 25+ Color palettes.<br></li><li> 15+ Player colors.<br></li><li> Endless and Boss Rush mode.<br></li><li> Chill Fishing mode.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Crushed!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1946460/c3ff7d4b895b22b01710d3e76ff23ee06f515f6f.jpg"},{"name":"Lambda","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1946460/148a07d1e4f28f023ebcb235d34d8782768f314f.jpg"},{"name":"Ocean Man","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1946460/9a9033b54c6bb7c9e5b271787c70de06d693fd1d.jpg"},{"name":"All Aboard!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1946460/84cbab40a02fe8f72371bafff0c8f5d5f7db3cca.jpg"},{"name":"Heads Up!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1946460/c2fbe70945f5b716b7704360e0638fea8780a5c7.jpg"},{"name":"Launched!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1946460/586116e775c5acf1c5d549b4697ec4fb3cf63461.jpg"},{"name":"Impaled!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1946460/a95732171c8da915ad15417ed1d286ed8a7ac829.jpg"},{"name":"Detected!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1946460/56b78958662b00b06e1ce678be13c60059ba68e5.jpg"},{"name":"Guppy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1946460/2b48f46d2a177c00e80b8a0d34f29a5031282ea6.jpg"},{"name":"Salmon","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1946460/c44bd752e9ee5cfda0bdb07311eb9a9083f96132.jpg"}],"total":20},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946460/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1671818438","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1946460/page.bg.jpg?